                                alt="April 2020"
                                width="105" />
                            </figure>
                        
                            <h2 class="hed">April 2020</h2>
                        </a>
                        
                            <p class="dek"> How to destroy a government, tackling giraffes, and does Reiki work? Plus a Colorado murder, capitalisms addiction problem, Michael Pollan on coffee, premiocrity, fallibility, weirdos, Hilary Mantel, and more. </p>
                        
                    </li>
                
                
                    <li class=" article" id="back-issue-5" >
