                        </a>
                        
                            <p class="dek"> The 2020 disinformation war, David Brooks on the nuclear family, #MeToo and the abortion-rights movement, and new fiction by Samantha Hunt. Plus trusting Nate Silver, the Supreme Courts enduring bias, climate change and peer pressure, an ode to cold showers, and more. </p>
                        
                    </li>
                
                
                    <li class=" article" id="back-issue-6" >
