                            <h2 class="hed">Jan/Feb 2020</h2>
                        </a>
                        
                            <p class="dek"> The miseducation of the American boy, John Hendrickson on Joe Bidens stutter, 20,000 feet under the sea, and a thriving conservative-Catholic community in Kansas. Plus Charlize Theron, Silicon Valleys failure to deliver, the myth of free shipping, how flamenco went pop, and more. </p>
                        
                    </li>
                
                
                    <li class=" article" id="back-issue-7" >
                        <a href="/magazine/toc/2019/12/" title="December 2019"
