                                alt="November 2019"
                                width="105" />
                            </figure>
                        
                            <h2 class="hed">November 2019</h2>
                        </a>
                        
                            <p class="dek"> The Tech Issue: Jeff Bezoss master plan, when GoFundMe gets ugly, and why the world is getting louder. Plus Mark Bowden on what military generals think of Trump, Jack Goldsmiths family and government surveillance, Sandra Boynton, baseball cards, why you never see your friends, and more. </p>
                        
                    </li>
                
                
                    <li class=" article" id="back-issue-9" >
                        <a href="/magazine/toc/2019/10/" title="October 2019"
